The Cut Django App: Pages



============
thecut.pages
============

To install this application (whilst in the project's activated
virtualenv)::
    pip install git+ssh://git@git.thecut.net.au/thecut-pages@0.04#egg=pages


Add the ``thecut.pages`` to the project's ``INSTALLED_APPS`` setting::

    INSTALLED_PAGES = (
        ...
        'thecut.pages',
    )


Add the ``thecut.pages.middleware.PageMiddleware`` to the end
(but before any RedirectFallbackMiddleware) of the project's
``MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES`` setting::

    MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES = (
        ...
        'thecut.pages.middleware.PageMiddleware',
        'django.contrib.redirects.middleware.RedirectFallbackMiddleware',
    )

